'''Damaged Package''' is a [[Quest Item]] obtained through exploration in [[Tequemecan Valley]]. This item is used in the [[Hidden Exploration Objective]] ''[[Lost Packages Retrieval]]''. Showing this item to [[NPC]] [[Michica]] changes it into [[Acat's Package]].
